data.description: Beautiful park like setting. Secluded and Private but just minute from Carthage-Webb City and Joplin. gorgeous wood throughout the home including the ceilings. Built in desktop and gun safe in MB. Lots of storage. 40x30 shop has plumbing stubbed in for apartment. There is a storm shelter as well.
